com.streethawk.library.push

Interface ISHObserver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppService

    public interface ISHObserver
    Interface for handling Raw JSON. App developer can implement this interface in activity or service to handle Raw JSON sent from Streethawk web console.
